videos.description: Illinois running back Mike Epstein finds a hole and flies 43 yards to the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Illinois RB breaks loose for 43-yard TD

videos.description: Illinois quarterback M.J. Rivers II and running back Reggie Corbin botch a handoff exchange, fumbling just outside of the red zone.
videos.headline: Illinois' drive stalls with fumble

videos.description: Illinois linebacker Del'Shawn Phillips intercepts a Blake Barnett pass and throws off tacklers as he trots 34 yards on the return into USF territory.
videos.headline: Illinois LB tosses tacklers on INT return

videos.description: USF quarterback Blake Barnett rolls left, throws across his body and connects with wide receiver Darnell Salomon for a 14-yard touchdown to pull within five of Illinois.
videos.headline: USF opens 4th with pretty TD

videos.description: Rams wide receiver Randall St. Felix shows shades of Randy Moss by climbing the ladder to reel in a 55-yard reception.
videos.headline: USF WR channels inner Randy Moss for 55-yard snag
